    "The scores show no significant difference in Accuracy, Breadth, Frustration, Effort, and Mental Demand.",
    "Ts group participants reported higher Physical Demand and Temporal Demand, while Baseline group participants reported higher Performance, reflecting a higher confidence in their generated outline.of LLMs.",
